{"tid":1579120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國旗最新版","createTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T17:06:47.000Z","uid":287740,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b90abaf2277541374287c913cca3f05a624fb7","tid":1579120,"uid":287740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"利申覺得前post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559834/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559834/page/1</a>) 支旗唔錯，但有以下缺點：<br />\n1. 有coat of arms 版顯得太過戀殖，而且太複雜好難簡單咁畫出嚟<br />\n2. 但係唔落coat of arms 辨識度又太低，容易同其他國家撈亂<br />\n3. 細節未落實 (準確嚟講係咩色咩比例？)<br />\n所以大膽提出以下嘅新設計<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMp58P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMp58P.jpg&h=1d8765a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比例<br />\n國旗用2:1比例，代表沿襲英國民主法治制度<br />\n<br />\n顏色<br />\n純白<br />\n本民前紫藍 (圖右；Pantone 10427C; RGB 40 60 127; 非圖左英國旗Union Jack深藍)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPPjaAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPPjaAG.jpg&h=12f2714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n構圖<br />\n白色部分置中，闊度為旗闊的1/6<br />\n抽象表現香港地理環境：上下深色色塊為香港島和九龍新界，中間白色為維港<br />\n<br />\n寓意<br />\n藍：代表自由、海港<br />\n白：代表平等、希望之光<br />\nWhite on Blue: 願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n優勢<br />\n設計簡單但唔會同其他國旗重覆，而且清楚代表香港及其立國理念<br />\n<br />\n有關啓發<br />\nBarnett Newman (1905-1970)，美國抽象表現主義的重要代表。他嘗試以他的畫作作出抗爭，破壞舊有秩序並同時建立新世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVNkECm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVNkECm.jpg&h=3d90feb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nBarnett Newman, Onement VI (1953)<br />\n<br />\nSVG檔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/pqruzp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2Fpqruzp&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=bc5227e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/pqruzp</a><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwEbMh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwEbMh6.jpg&h=3ef9608f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21727411aa7246b8ce41f8ee2d12cc04a745a489","tid":1579120,"uid":10788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"無共嗚"},{"pid":"af4faa88eb421df65534b2aa2d2873c5b7fa2f0d","tid":1579120,"uid":282897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0b90abaf2277541374287c913cca3f05a624fb7","tid":1579120,"uid":287740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"利申覺得前post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559834/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559834/page/1</a>) 支旗唔錯，但有以下缺點：<br />\n1. 有coat of arms 版顯得太過戀殖，而且太複雜好難簡單咁畫出嚟<br />\n2. 但係唔落coat of arms 辨識度又太低，容易同其他國家撈亂<br />\n3. 細節未落實 (準確嚟講係咩色咩比例？)<br />\n所以大膽提出以下嘅新設計<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMp58P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMp58P.jpg&h=1d8765a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比例<br />\n國旗用2:1比例，代表沿襲英國民主法治制度<br />\n<br />\n顏色<br />\n純白<br />\n本民前紫藍 (圖右；Pantone 10427C; RGB 40 60 127; 非圖左英國旗Union Jack深藍)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPPjaAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPPjaAG.jpg&h=12f2714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n構圖<br />\n白色部分置中，闊度為旗闊的1/6<br />\n抽象表現香港地理環境：上下深色色塊為香港島和九龍新界，中間白色為維港<br />\n<br />\n寓意<br />\n藍：代表自由、海港<br />\n白：代表平等、希望之光<br />\nWhite on Blue: 願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n優勢<br />\n設計簡單但唔會同其他國旗重覆，而且清楚代表香港及其立國理念<br />\n<br />\n有關啓發<br />\nBarnett Newman (1905-1970)，美國抽象表現主義的重要代表。他嘗試以他的畫作作出抗爭，破壞舊有秩序並同時建立新世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVNkECm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVNkECm.jpg&h=3d90feb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nBarnett Newman, Onement VI (1953)<br />\n<br />\nSVG檔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/pqruzp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2Fpqruzp&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=bc5227e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/pqruzp</a><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwEbMh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwEbMh6.jpg&h=3ef9608f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"戀殖? 無英國管治, 邊有香港."},{"pid":"26b0e6638c9e729e2f6a8f38f4292ac8d0f93a9b","tid":1579120,"uid":69753,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"大家都知只有一個真正嘅旗&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0NOjVhY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0NOjVhY.png&h=2dcabe0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他嘅，自己屋企攞嚟打飛機算罷"},{"pid":"f6bc687a760dacc0ea4d418e3126e23e8451bb80","tid":1579120,"uid":271337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"覺得呢個顏色分佈pattern 唔錯  幾靚仔   但選色上都係㨂番黑同黃會係呢個時間有共嗚啲同埋回應當下時局"},{"pid":"a62b00a4cfea6ddb267e6069f9696884a4d2ed14","tid":1579120,"uid":253886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JshMGQZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJshMGQZ.gif&h=46f7e04c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b11316836f42455243c116dd54a2221ccc326ae6","tid":1579120,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"［集中討論。求同存異］點先可以揀到一支香港旗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581181</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11e62b3518b69ef054cdb57eff9ee877f01d0bf9","tid":1579120,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"最落力既都唔係97